{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59051B0324P2D1N000079", "chronotag": "1739874562410", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "II-CL79", "numeroOrdreDepot": "79", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_LOIS", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59051B0324P2D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0324", "triAmendement": "aeoaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaay", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA794502", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845401", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Taverne"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "\u00c9TAT B", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 42", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 42", "type": "ANNEXE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": "ARTICLE 42", "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0324C.asp#D_Etat_B"}, "missionVisee": {"codeEtat": "B", "codeMissionMinefi": "SB", "libelleMission": "S\u00e9curit\u00e9s", "missionRef": "2896"}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositifAmdtCreditPLF": {"listeProgrammes": {"programme": [{"libelle": "Police nationale", "programmeRef": "380830", "autorisationEngagement": "20000000", "creditPaiement": "20000000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Gendarmerie nationale", "programmeRef": "380832", "autorisationEngagement": "-20000000", "creditPaiement": "-20000000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"ligneCredit": {"id": "10354", "libelle": "dont titre 2", "autorisationEngagement": "-20000000", "creditPaiement": "-20000000", "action": "modification"}}}, {"libelle": "S\u00e9curit\u00e9 et \u00e9ducation routi\u00e8res", "programmeRef": "380834", "autorisationEngagement": "0", "creditPaiement": "0", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "S\u00e9curit\u00e9 civile", "programmeRef": "380836", "autorisationEngagement": "0", "creditPaiement": "0", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}]}, "soldeAE": "0", "soldeCP": "0", "cpEgalAe": "true"}, "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Le manque de formation au sein de nos forces de l'ordre est une probl&#x00E9;matique connue et cet enjeu doit &#x00EA;tre une priorit&#x00E9; du Minist&#x00E8;re de l'Int&#x00E9;rieur.</p><p>Or, lors du PLF 2024, et contrairement aux engagements du pr&#x00E9;c&#x00E9;dent Ministre de l'Int&#x00E9;rieur, les cr&#x00E9;dits allou&#x00E9;s &#x00E0; la formation avaient diminu&#x00E9; de 31,49%.</p><p>Toutefois, la fusion de la sous-action intitul&#x00E9;e &#x00AB; Formation&nbsp;&#x00BB; au sein d'une sous-action plus large intitul&#x00E9;e &#x00AB; Fonctionnement courant des services &#x00BB; ne permet pas de s'assurer qu'un effort ait v&#x00E9;ritablement &#x00E9;t&#x00E9; fait cette ann&#x00E9;e en ce sens.</p><p>Il appara&#x00EE;t donc n&#x00E9;cessaire - a minima - d'annuler la baisse des cr&#x00E9;dits allou&#x00E9;s &#x00E0; la formation vot&#x00E9;e en 2024, et d'augmenter sensiblement ce budget.</p><p>De fait, le pr&#x00E9;sent amendement propose d&#x2019;abonder la sous-action 06-01 &#x00AB; Fonctionnement courant des services&nbsp;&#x00BB;, qui comprend la formation, de l&#x2019;action 06 &#x00AB; Commandement, ressources humaines et logistique &#x00BB; du programme 176 &#x00AB; Police nationale &#x00BB; de 20 millions d&#x2019;euros en autorisations d&#x2019;engagement et en cr&#x00E9;dits de paiement, et pour des raisons de recevabilit&#x00E9; financi&#x00E8;re de diminuer du m&#x00EA;me montant les autorisations d&#x2019;engagement et les cr&#x00E9;dits de paiement de la sous-action 02-01 &#x00AB;S&#x00E9;curit&#x00E9; routi&#x00E8;re - hors administration centrale et cabinet &#x00BB; de l&#x2019;action 02 &#x00AB; S&#x00E9;curit&#x00E9; routi&#x00E8;re &#x00BB; du programme 152 &#x00AB; Gendarmerie nationale &#x00BB;. <u></u></p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-10-18", "datePublication": "2024-11-15", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Rejet\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-10-22T22:35:02+02:00", "sort": "Rejet\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59051B0324P2D1N000079?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "1", "divisionCodeLoi": "10 formation policiers"}, "discussionCommune": {"idDiscussion": "25950", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}